         <abstract id="aspace_16222b410f77e3732689afd77d3114f4">The papers consist of student notebooks, syllabi, and other course materials belonging to Mercedes Moore DeMare, a 1936 M.F.A. graduate of the drama program in the Yale University School of the Fine Arts.</abstract>
